c: 4
v: 100
t: "Iye amene asamuka kwawo mu njira ya Mulungu adzapeza padziko lapansi malo ochuluka othawirako ndi katundu wochuluka. Ndipo iye amene asamuka chifukwa cha Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake ndipo imfa impeza, ndithu malipiro ake ali ndi Mulungu. Ndipo Mulungu ndi wokhululuka ndi wachisoni chosatha"